1
04:05:30,641 --> 04:05:32,516
The Eagles are coming.

2
04:06:22,818 --> 04:06:23,818
Bilbo.

3
04:06:23,860 --> 04:06:25,819
Don't move. Don't move. Lie still.

4
04:06:27,489 --> 04:06:30,032
Oh. Mm. Mm.

5
04:06:30,409 --> 04:06:31,534
I'm glad you are here.

6
04:06:31,784 --> 04:06:33,327
- Shh, shh.
- Unh.

7
04:06:34,288 --> 04:06:36,079
I wish to part from you in friendship.

8
04:06:36,331 --> 04:06:37,331
No.

9
04:06:37,416 --> 04:06:38,791
You are not going anywhere.

10
04:06:39,542 --> 04:06:40,877
You're going to live.

11
04:06:41,336 --> 04:06:42,336
I would take back...

12
04:06:42,587 --> 04:06:44,422
...my words and my deeds at the Gate.

13
04:06:46,257 --> 04:06:48,676
You did what only a true friend would do.

14
04:06:50,136 --> 04:06:51,136
Forgive me.

15
04:06:53,931 --> 04:06:56,016
I was too blind to see it.

16
04:06:58,395 --> 04:06:59,936
I am so sorry...

17
04:07:01,315 --> 04:07:03,190
...that I have led you into such peril.

18
04:07:04,359 --> 04:07:07,110
No, I'm glad to have shared
in your perils, Thorin.

19
04:07:07,361 --> 04:07:08,654
Each and every one of them.

20
04:07:12,074 --> 04:07:15,035
It is far more than any Baggins deserves.

21
04:07:19,458 --> 04:07:20,458
Farewell...

22
04:07:21,584 --> 04:07:23,377
...Master Burglar.

23
04:07:24,712 --> 04:07:26,756
Go back to your books.

24
04:07:27,925 --> 04:07:29,926
And your armchair.

25
04:07:31,677 --> 04:07:33,596
Plant your trees.

26
04:07:34,264 --> 04:07:35,931
Watch them grow.

27
04:07:40,979 --> 04:07:42,730
If more people...

28
04:07:43,774 --> 04:07:45,399
...valued home...

29
04:07:45,650 --> 04:07:47,609
...above gold...

30
04:07:48,611 --> 04:07:52,198
...this world would be a merrier place.

31
04:07:55,993 --> 04:07:58,287
No. No, no, no. No.

32
04:07:58,538 --> 04:08:00,957
Thorin. Thorin, don't you dare.

33
04:08:03,252 --> 04:08:04,377
Thorin.

34
04:08:10,342 --> 04:08:12,717
Thorin. Thorin, hold on.

35
04:08:12,970 --> 04:08:14,136
Hold on, please.

36
04:08:14,680 --> 04:08:15,846
The Eagles...

37
04:08:16,515 --> 04:08:18,724
The Eagles... The Eagles are here.

38
04:08:19,392 --> 04:08:20,560
Thorin?

39
04:08:23,771 --> 04:08:24,896
The Ea...

